# ============================================================================
# WHAT GHOSTTY DOES BETTER (Out of the Box)
# ============================================================================
#
# 1. AUTO THEME SWITCHING
#    WezTerm: Needs custom Lua function + window-config-reloaded hook
#    Ghostty: Built-in → theme = dark,light
#
# 2. FONT RENDERING
#    WezTerm: Needs freetype_load_target + freetype_render_target
#    Ghostty: Perfect by default with macOS Core Text
#
# 3. COPY ON SELECT
#    WezTerm: Needs custom mouse_bindings table
#    Ghostty: Built-in → copy-on-select = true
#
# 4. PERFORMANCE
#    WezTerm: ~150MB memory, WebGPU overhead
#    Ghostty: ~90MB memory, native rendering
#
# 5. SHELL INTEGRATION
#    WezTerm: Limited, needs external setup
#    Ghostty: Built-in, automatic detection
#
# 6. MACOS FEATURES
#    WezTerm: Good but generic (cross-platform tool)
#    Ghostty: Excellent, macOS-first design
#
# 7. CONFIG SIMPLICITY
#    WezTerm: Lua programming, 220+ lines
#    Ghostty: Simple key=value, cleaner defaults
